InfoAppDescription: Wrap App is the app for creating of a texture that allows to create the wrap for an object from scratch, upload image from your computed, check created wrap on the 3D model and download the wrap to the future using.
InfoLinesDescriptions: 'Draw' function helps you to add straight or free lines with defined color.
InfoFiguresDescriptions: Using 'Figures' function, you can add any figure from the list with selected lines color, filling and thickness.
InfoIconsDescription: 'Icons' function propose to add various figures using selected border color.
InfoTextDescription: 'Text' section allows to add text to the wrap using different style, alignment and color.
InfoImageDescription: 'Load image' function allows to upload an image from your computer, that can be used as a part of your wrap or placed on the whole area.
InfoFiltersDescription: 'Filters' section helps to change color shades or brightness of the whole texture.
InfoModelDescription: Created wrap can be applied to the model using 'Check on model' button. Function 'Start/Stop' starts model rotating to check created texture on the 3D model. You can download created wrap to your computer using 'Download texture' button
